title: [PSP] 3.90 M33-3 Custom Firmware Pack
description:
3.90 M33-3 Custom Firmware Pack


   Includes:

      - 3.90 M33-3 by Dark~AleX with the 390.PBP included in the installer.

      - 3.71 fatmsmod patch v2 by Dark~AleX with fatmsmod.prx included.

      - 3.80 popsloader plugin v2 by Dark~AleX (compatible with 3.90 M33-3) including all firmware modules.

      - 1.50 kernel add-on v2 for 3.90 M33 by Dark~AleX (can only be used on Fat/PSP-1000 models).

      - MAC Address spoofer plugin by Dark~AleX.

      - CWCheat 2.2.0 Revision B by Wetall.

      - Alternative VSHMenu 4.2 by Red Squirrel.

      - Savegame Deemer v1.10 by HELLCAT (save and load unencrypted Savedata so they can be Hex-edited).

Note: This requires to have 3.52 M33-4 or higher firmware. Will not work on official firmware.
